<body>
The use of an off-hand weapon greatly reduces the fighter's ability to<br>
avoid an opponent's attack.  After years of practice with off-hand<br>
attacks, the warrior/ranger begins to learn how to actually parry with<br>
his/her off-hand weapon.  Although not as effective as a shield, it does<br>
reduce the damage taken in battle.  This is an autoskill.<br>
